long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allhomes and Zango are websites that list real estates for sale in Australia. They provide various filters for filtering listings. However, they do not provide filter for "Energy Efficiency Rating" (EER), which is specified in most listings.

This extension allows the user to filter listings on Allhomes and Zango based on a preset EER.
